{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发送了消息:\"[图片]\"\n^system:20260303_085501:这张图片的内容是：例 6.2.5 求微分方程 y' = (y-x)/(y+x) 的通解.","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260303_085501"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260303_085506"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260303_085529"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:看到了！是求微分方程 $y' = \\frac{y-x}{y+x}$ 的通解对吧？\n这是一个齐次微分方程哦。\n我们可以令 $y = ux$，那么 $y' = u + x \\frac{du}{dx}$。\n代入方程后：$u + x \\frac{du}{dx} = \\frac{ux-x}{ux+x} = \\frac{u-1}{u+1}$。\n整理一下：$x \\frac{du}{dx} = \\frac{u-1}{u+1} - u = \\frac{u-1-u^2-u}{u+1} = -\\frac{u^2+1}{u+1}$。\n分离变量：$\\frac{u+1}{u^2+1} du = -\\frac{1}{x} dx$。\n两边积分：$\\int \\frac{u}{u^2+1} du + \\int \\frac{1}{u^2+1} du = -\\int \\frac{1}{x} dx$。\n得到：$\\frac{1}{2}\\ln(u^2+1) + \\arctan u = -\\ln|x| + C$。\n最后把 $u = \\frac{y}{x}$ 代回去：$\\frac{1}{2}\\ln(\\frac{y^2}{x^2}+1) + \\arctan(\\frac{y}{x}) + \\ln|x| = C$。\n化简一下就是：$\\frac{1}{2}\\ln(x^2+y^2) + \\arctan(\\frac{y}{x}) = C$。\n岛岛你看，是这个结果吗？如果有哪一步觉得奇怪可以问我哦！","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260303_085535"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发送了消息:\"QQ不支持markdown消息啊\"","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260303_085535"}
